OL,3,CScottish man faces 22 years in prison
OL,4,Cover #5.9m US cyber fraud scheme
OL,6,FA Scottish man has pleaded guilty to
OL,7,Fplotting to hack into the computer
OL,8,Fsystems of at least a dozen companies
OL,9,Fto steal at least $8 million (around
OL,10,F#5.9 million) in virtual currency from
OL,11,Fvictims in the United States.
OL,13,FThe US Department of Justice (DOJ)
OL,14,Fsaid Tyler Buchanan, 24, from Dundee,
OL,15,Fwas involved in a group that used text
OL,16,Fmessage phishing attacks to trick
OL,17,Femployees into disclosing their login
OL,18,Fcredentials, enabling access to
OL,19,Fcomputer systems.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
