OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776553377
OL,3,CScottish man faces 22 years in prison
OL,4,Cover #5.9m US cyber fraud scheme
OL,6,FBuchanan pleaded guilty to one count
OL,7,Fof conspiracy to commit wire fraud and
OL,8,Fone count of aggravated identity theft.
OL,10,FUS officials said he and his co-
OL,11,Fconspirators sent hundreds of messages
OL,12,Fto company employees, posing as the
OL,13,Fcompanies or their contracted
OL,14,Fsuppliers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776553377
OL,3,CScottish man faces 22 years in prison
OL,4,Cover #5.9m US cyber fraud scheme
OL,6,FIn his plea agreement, the 24-year-old
OL,7,Fadmitted that between September 2021
OL,8,Fand April 2023, the group planned to
OL,9,Fscam telecommunications companies, IT
OL,10,Fsuppliers, cloud communications
OL,11,Fproviders, virtual currency firms and
OL,12,Findividuals.
OL,14,FA device seized at Buchanan's home in
OL,15,FScotland showed he possessed the names
OL,16,Fand addresses of multiple victims, as
OL,17,Fwell as a text file containing
OL,18,Fcryptocurrency seed phrases and login
OL,19,Fcredentials for one victim's account.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
