OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776553377
OL,3,CScottish man faces 22 years in prison
OL,4,Cover #5.9m US cyber fraud scheme
OL,6,F"The conspirators created a phishing
OL,7,Fkit that captured login credentials
OL,8,Fentered into the fraudulent phishing
OL,9,Fwebsites by a victim company's
OL,10,Femployees," the DOJ said in a
OL,11,Fstatement.
OL,13,F"The stolen credentials were then
OL,14,Ftransmitted to an online Telegram
OL,15,Fchannel administered by Buchanan and
OL,16,Fanother co-conspirator."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@KO]uD@AOUxD@XO]
