OL,3,CScottish man faces 22 years in prison
OL,4,Cover #5.9m US cyber fraud scheme
OL,6,FBuchanan has been in US federal
OL,7,Fcustody since April 2025. He is
OL,8,Fscheduled to be sentenced on August 21
OL,9,Fand faces a maximum sentence of 22
OL,10,Fyears in prison.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FThree other defendants, all from the
OL,18,FUnited States, are still facing
OL,19,Fcriminal charges, according to the DOJ.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
