OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776553377
OL,3,CScottish man faces 22 years in prison
OL,4,Cover #5.9m US cyber fraud scheme
OL,6,FAnother co-conspirator, Noah Michael
OL,7,FUrban, pleaded guilty in April 2025 to
OL,8,Fthree fraud-related charges and is
OL,9,Fserving a 10-year prison sentence.
OL,11,FUrban was also ordered to pay 13
OL,12,Fmillion dollars (#9.6 million) in
OL,13,Frestitution.
OL,15,FThe DOJ said Police Scotland was one
OL,16,Fof several agencies providing the FBI
OL,17,Fwith assistance as they carried out
OL,18,Fthe investigation.
